Harold’s Place
We’d like to welcome all of the people from around the world who have enjoyed our wonderful restaurant.
If you’re a newbie, you’re in for a treat. For more than 33 years, Harold’s Place has been the bar and grill of choice in SW Florida.
Discover our Chickee Bar! In a lush tropical setting, overlooking our beautiful pool.
Serving the Charbroiled Award Winning “Best Burger” in Southwest Florida, Real Gulf Grouper, Daily Homemade specials and “Full Service Bar”
Happy Hour from 4:00 p.m till 7:00 p.m. Monday through Friday.
Phone (239) 263-7254
